\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Prior dominance vs.\ pattern blindness isolated on the same model (\texttt  {gpt-4o}). \textbf  {A}: \texttt  {gpt-4o} correctly inverts logic with explicit rule (L3). \textbf  {B}: The same model reverts to Python prior when the rule is embedded only in examples (L4). This contrast isolates pattern blindness as a failure mode distinct from prior dominance.}}{8}{}\protected@file@percent }
